OL,3,CFather says blaze which killed his
OL,4,Cwife and three children 'destroyed my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FA father whose wife and three children
OL,8,Fwere killed in a house blaze in west
OL,9,FLondon believed to have been caused by
OL,10,Fa firework has told how the night
OL,11,F"destroyed my life" as he warned "if
OL,12,Fyou use fireworks, you could lose
OL,13,Feverything".
OL,15,FAroen Kishen had been celebrating
OL,16,FDiwali with his wife Seema, their
OL,17,Fchildren Riyan, 11, and Arohi, eight,
OL,18,Fand four-year-old Shanaya, and family
OL,19,Ffriends at their home in Hounslow in
OL,20,FNovember 2023.
