OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FNearly two years on, ahead of Diwali
OL,8,Fon Monday, Mr Kishen has told of the
OL,9,Fhorror of the evening when his family
OL,10,Fhome became engulfed in flames.
OL,12,F"That night, I lost my wife Seema, our
OL,13,Fthree children Riyan, Arohi, Shanaya,
OL,14,Fand two family friends, Nitin and
OL,15,FSandiya (Chopra)," Mr Kishen said.
OL,17,F"I wish they were still alive because
OL,18,Fwhat happened that night destroyed my
OL,19,Flife."
