OL,7,FLondon Fire Brigade (LFB) believes the
OL,8,Fmost probable cause of the fire was a
OL,9,Ffirework igniting combustible
OL,10,Frecycling waste in a plastic recycling
OL,11,Fbin next to the house.
OL,13,FIt is not known where the firework
OL,14,Fcame from.
OL,16,FA coroner ruled in the inquest into
OL,17,Ftheir deaths earlier this year that
OL,18,Fthe six people died in a "tragic
OL,19,Faccident", having been "very quickly
OL,20,Foverwhelmed by smoke fumes", LFB said.
