OL,4,Cwife and three children 'destroyed my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FMr Kishen said: "Diwali in 2023
OL,8,Fstarted as a normal day with my
OL,9,Ffamily. In the afternoon we prayed at
OL,10,Fhome together, then we went to the
OL,11,Fgurdwara in Southall and visited with
OL,12,Fsome family nearby. We all had dinner
OL,13,Ftogether and put the children to bed
OL,14,Fready for school the next day.
OL,16,F"Shortly after that, I saw the fire. I
OL,17,Ftried to go upstairs to help my
OL,18,Ffamily, but I lost consciousness. I
OL,19,Fdon't know what happened after that.
OL,20,FWhen I woke up, the whole house was on
OL,21,Ffire."
