OL,7,FThe inquest heard that Mr Kishen was
OL,8,F"heroic", LFB said, when he attempted
OL,9,Fto tackle the fire and sustained burns
OL,10,Fbefore he lost consciousness.
OL,12,FWhen he regained consciousness, the
OL,13,Ffire had spread.
OL,15,FFirefighters arrived at around 10.30pm
OL,16,Fon November 12 2023 and crews were
OL,17,Fable to reach the first floor but were
OL,18,Fforced to retreat because of the
OL,19,Fseverity of the fire.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@HO]
