OL,7,FAnother team then tried to tackle the
OL,8,Fblaze on the first floor but faced
OL,9,Fsimilar issues and as they went
OL,10,Fdownstairs the internal staircase
OL,11,Fpartly collapsed.
OL,13,FAround 70 firefighters dealt with the
OL,14,Fblaze which spread from the ground
OL,15,Ffloor to the roof.
OL,17,FMr Kishen has urged people think about
OL,18,Fthose around them before they use
OL,19,Ffireworks, warning that they "aren't a
OL,20,Fgame".
OL,26,@{D@^OU|D@EO]
