OL,3,CFather says blaze which killed his
OL,4,Cwife and three children 'destroyed my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FThe bereaved father said: "I want the
OL,8,Fpublic to think about those around
OL,9,Fthem before using fireworks.
OL,11,F"Fireworks aren't a game and it's not
OL,12,Fa movie, it's real life.
OL,14,F"Listen to my story and celebrate with
OL,15,Fyour family, at a party or at your
OL,16,Fplace of worship.
OL,18,F"If you use fireworks, you could lose
OL,19,Feverything."
OL,26,@oD@[OUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU{D@LO]
