OL,7,FThe fire happened during what was
OL,8,FLFB's busiest Diwali since 2010.
OL,10,FOver the 24-hour period, control
OL,11,Fofficers took 710 emergency calls and
OL,12,Fhandled 17 firework-related calls and
OL,13,Fincidents, LFB said.
OL,15,FPaul Askew, the brigade's deputy
OL,16,Fassistant commissioner, said: "On
OL,17,Fbehalf of London Fire Brigade, I'd
OL,18,Flike to express my condolences to Mr
OL,19,FKishen and all of those affected by
OL,20,Fthis terrible tragedy.
OL,26,@xD@_OU
