OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,F"On what was meant to be a night of
OL,8,Fcelebration to mark the beginning of
OL,9,FDiwali, a tragic accident occurred.
OL,11,F"I'd like to thank in particular the
OL,12,Fbravery of the initial crews on scene,
OL,13,Fwho were faced with a devastating
OL,14,Fhouse fire.
OL,16,F"This incident sadly highlights the
OL,17,Fdangers that we know exist with
OL,18,Ffireworks.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
