OL,3,CFather says blaze which killed his
OL,4,Cwife and three children 'destroyed my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,F"We're urging Londoners to listen to
OL,8,FMr Kishen's story and follow our
OL,9,Fadvice by attending a safer, organised
OL,10,Ffireworks display this year."
OL,12,FHe stressed that people who intend to
OL,13,Fhost their own display should buy
OL,14,Ffireworks from a reputable seller with
OL,15,Fa CE safety mark, and secure them
OL,16,Fproperly in the ground, far from
OL,17,Fbuildings, trees and animals.
OL,19,F"As we approach Diwali, Halloween and
OL,20,FBonfire Night, we wish everyone a safe
OL,21,Ffireworks season," he added.
